title: ESIC Recruitment 2025 - Walk-in-Interview for 95 Senior Resident Posts
description: The Employees' State Insurance Corporation (ESIC) has published the official notification for 2025. To fill up the 95 vacancies for Senior Resident Jobs. Those candidates who have qualified in the MBBS, MD/ MS can grab this chance and apply for the ESIC Recruitment 2025 . Here, we provided more information about the age limit, selection process, salary structure, education details, application fee, and how to apply for these posts.
